data.description: Great price! Pretty views! Welcome home to this spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with 1,952 sq ft and true pride of ownership. Enter to soaring ceiling, gorgeous tiles floors, subtle papers and paints, and views towards the Topa Topa Mountains. Your Living Room has high cathedral ceilings and a fireplace. The kitchen features oak cabinetry, tile counters, and stainless appliances and opens to the Dining Area with views. Newer windows and patio sliders have been installed throughout. Newer water heater. There is a downstairs bedroom or den with a walk-in closet and full bathroom. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms with mountain views. The primary bedroom is oversized with so much closet space. The gated courtyard entry provides privacy and opens to two patios. There's plenty of room to garden and spend time outdoors. Lower gardens are a few steps down and extends your space. So many options here, grapes, citrus, vegetables, ?  Located on a small cul-de-sac with the community pool nearby,  Kelly Park is a small enclave of homes in Newbury Park close to shopping, restaurants, and easy 101 access.
